html.div:
Default palette
Standard palette1 — no accessibility mode set. {{ charts['default'] }}
Color Blind Modes
Set via theme.accessibility.colorBlindMode. Each palette is designed to remain distinguishable under the named color vision deficiency.
Deuteranopia
Red-green (green-weak) · ~6% of males {{ charts['deuteranopia'] }}
Protanopia
Red-green (red-weak) · ~1% of males {{ charts['protanopia'] }}
Tritanopia
Blue-yellow · ~0.01% of population {{ charts['tritanopia'] }}
High Contrast
Wider strokes · data labels always on {{ charts['highContrast'] }}

